import personalHeadshot from '../../assets/images/headshot3.png';

/* For the about me section on the front page */
export const aboutMe = {
    reverseColumns: false,

    exactClassName: 'hero-section hero-section-aboutme aboutmeBg',
    rowClass: 'row hero-row hero-aboutme',
    colClass: 'col',
    flexDirection: 'row',
    textWrapper: 'hero-text-wrapper hero-text-wrapper-aboutme',
    topLineClass: 'top-line top-line-aboutme',
    headlineClass: 'heading heading-aboutme',
    descriptionClass: 'hero-subtitle dark',
    displayButtonBool: true,
    imgWrapper: 'hero-img-wrapper',
    imgStart: '',
    heroimg: true,
    imgClass: 'hero-img hero-img-aboutme',

    topLine: '',
    headline: 'Sarah Collins',
    description:    
    "Hello! I am a recent Spring 2021 graduate from Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University with a Bachelor's of Science in \
     Software Engineering, seeking an entry-level role within the gaming industry.",
    img: personalHeadshot,
    alt: 'Personal Headshot'

  };
